item.title: MIDWEEK RUB | Max King's knee, Dusty's future, how's Joey's Carlton Draft training going?
item.description:
Joey, Daisy and Damo are back to to discuss all the biggest news and views in footy, including Joey's (lack of) training regime ahead of his Carlton Draft appearance, Max King's knee injury, Dustin Martin's future, Jordan Boyd's tribunal case, Fair Dinkum or Fugazi, round 17 predictions and more.
